# MiAyudaTIC Founder OS

> 6-role founding team. Human coordinates. **One role per task.**

**Entrypoint:** [`AGENTS.md`](AGENTS.md) — roles, subagents (`.cursor/agents/`), skills (`.cursor/skills/`), hooks, verify.

## Repo map

| Path | Surface |
|------|---------|
| `client/` | Web (Vercel) |
| `server/` | API (Render) |
| `mobile/MiAyudaTIC-Mobile/` | Official mobile (Expo) |
| `packages/contracts/` | `@miayuda/contracts` |
| `mobile_flutter/MBO_ULT/` | **LEGACY — do not extend** |

## Before coding

1. Read `AGENTS.md` and docs for your surface (`product.md`, `contracts.md`, `architecture.md`).
2. Declare scope (in / out) and pick subagent from `.cursor/agents/`.
3. Complete `docs/handoff-template.md` when done.

**Code truth:** `archive/audits/` when docs conflict with code.
